Class MockDouble

java.lang.Object
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model.MockDouble
All Implemented Interfaces:
IMatrix<Double>
public class MockDouble extends Object implements IMatrix<Double>
A class in the 'model' package. The class implements IMatrix interface with Double type and is used for testing purposes. It imitates Matrix class.
